{"tid":698103,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日ex帶埋條仔嚟我開工地方落我面","createTime":"2018-06-11T11:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T06:33:00.000Z","uid":5077,"like":3,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"667d76088907785cd4235c7b896e85e6bc82e30d","tid":698103,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:53:53.000Z","msg":"今日食飽飯諗住返上樓開工，<br />\n返到去無耐就已經有人㩒鐘，<br />\n一開門就見到個大隻南亞仔，<br />\n入到嚟問佢想點玩，佢就話玩開捆綁，<br />\n咁好啦照做啦反正佢係客，最多收佢貴啲，<br />\n點知佢玩到勁hardcore，<br />\n又拳打腳踢又痾屎痾尿落去到，<br />\n屌到我屎忽勁痛，<br />\n<br />\n俾佢折磨咗差唔多一個鐘之後，<br />\n突然間又有人㩒鐘，<br />\n原來係我ex上咗嚟，<br />\n<br />\n無計啦照做啦反正佢係客，<br />\n點知玩玩吓佢拎把刀出嚟，<br />\n對住我塊面係咁割係咁割，<br />\n割晒我塊面啲肉落嚟話要拎去煮飯，<br />\n我問佢地係咪窮到咁呀？<br />\n<br />\n佢話：無計啦我條仔係南亞人，無咩貢獻"},{"pid":"7abc1ec8eb41d5b2a47c7f70cb807d03e5ed2c46","tid":698103,"uid":136502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:09:40.000Z","msg":"其實....你想點？"},{"pid":"2d0ed29b5ee8f2e72ec7e8ed6e1439ebc7dbad27","tid":698103,"uid":176960,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:15:24.000Z","msg":"Ok,你想要負皮，我俾囉～"},{"pid":"3a30bef99081c058251c449cd2eba0fe999d9bfc","tid":698103,"uid":44562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:29:21.000Z","msg":"pass ! 唔洗重作了"},{"pid":"e57610dc7fac283bed9e852412aeae0123323a3e","tid":698103,"uid":47663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:31:36.000Z","msg":"辣殺"},{"pid":"c890f6f2a3075643f6c6168f16a944c1650b94ff","tid":698103,"uid":139974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"019bdeb648c1f77c3f0b618f7f1c69ffea9920b0","tid":698103,"uid":135060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:33:00.000Z","msg":"？？？"}]}